00:06:16,540 --> 00:06:20,700
Presumably then let us say that our impressions are the results of sense-statem, but actually

71
00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:26,540
the way we distinguish between those and our ideas, copies of impressions, is by their

72
00:06:26,540 --> 00:06:27,540
vivacity.

