00:06:30,380 --> 00:06:36,860
Your visual representation of me, when you look at me, is far more powerful and profound

75
00:06:36,860 --> 00:06:40,140
and sharp than is, say, your recollection of what I looked like.

76
00:06:40,140 --> 00:06:42,540
There's far more detail in the first class.

77
00:06:42,540 --> 00:06:47,780
So that's the first class of our mental representations, impressions, distinguished

78
00:06:47,780 --> 00:06:49,220
by their greater vivacity.

