00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:24,580
And the first of those is, of course, resemblance.

101
00:08:24,580 --> 00:08:25,580
Right?

102
00:08:25,580 --> 00:08:32,420
We say that the representation you have of me now strongly resembles the representation

