00:09:11,420 --> 00:09:16,380
The second is contiguity, right?

113
00:09:16,380 --> 00:09:22,900
All of our ideas can be related in terms of their spatial relationships or temporal relationships.

114
00:09:22,900 --> 00:09:28,860
So I am, from my perspective, to the right of the lectern presently and behind it.

115
00:09:28,860 --> 00:09:33,020
Now I'm to the left of the lectern and behind it, again, from my perspective.

116
00:09:33,380 --> 00:09:37,700
Similarly, the sentences I am pronouncing now follow the sentences I pronounced, say,

117
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:38,860
some one minute ago.

