00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:06,500
You attribute a causal agency.

126
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:08,500
Okay.

127
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:12,220
Now, we have all the principles of association.

128
00:10:12,220 --> 00:10:14,900
Let's now talk about our knowledge.

129
00:10:14,900 --> 00:10:19,660
And again, that can be broken down into one of two classes.

130
00:10:19,660 --> 00:10:26,220
The first class deals with the relations between ideas in a purely formal sense.

131
00:10:26,220 --> 00:10:32,460
A human such knowledge is either intuitively certain or, if not, it is demonstrable.

132
00:10:32,460 --> 00:10:34,580
Okay.

133
00:10:34,580 --> 00:10:37,020
So what would be examples?

