00:12:07,180 --> 00:12:12,220
Those propositions which concern existential statements are statements of fact.

152
00:12:12,220 --> 00:12:16,860
The first thing to note is that there is no logical basis for all of our knowledge of

153
00:12:16,860 --> 00:12:18,740
fact.

154
00:12:18,740 --> 00:12:19,940
And how do we know that?

155
00:12:19,940 --> 00:12:25,660
