00:12:35,020 --> 00:12:36,940
It never has, right?

160
00:12:36,940 --> 00:12:41,340
I've never observed that myself, but there is nothing that logically constrains this

161
00:12:41,340 --> 00:12:47,140
watch to either fall down or not to simply remain sustained in the air.

162
00:12:47,140 --> 00:12:49,940
If I was the amazing Kresge or something, I could do such a trick.

163
00:12:49,940 --> 00:12:56,140
But this point is, since counterfactuals are all logically possible, right, then there

164
00:12:56,140 --> 00:13:00,460
is no logical basis for knowledge of matters of fact.

