00:13:00,460 --> 00:13:05,700
Well, then that raises, for Hume, the critical epistemological question.

166
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:07,860
How do we know matters of fact?

167
00:13:07,860 --> 00:13:12,500
Specifically, how do we know any matters of fact other than that which you are presently

